seller.oneLinerTitle: Professional Animator: After Effects, SVG, Lottie, Rive, CSS, HTML, JS
seller.description:
Greetings,
I am Oleg, a seasoned motion designer with an extensive portfolio in creating dynamic content for Websites, Apps, Social and Media platforms.
Leveraging my expertise in Motion Design, SVG Animations, and proficiency in CSS, HTML, JavaScript, Lottie (JSON) and Rive,
I craft engaging Animated Web Elements, Site Preloaders, and Explainer Videos.
In addition, I offer Sound Design, Audio (mixing) services and Ukrainian Voice Over.
Feel free to browse my gigs and examples to understand the quality of work you can expect.
Let's collaborate and bring your vision to life!
